data.description: ***NEW GRANITE COUNTERS HAVE BEEN INSTALLED***Clean, well maintained, move in ready home! This open floor plan ensures that everyone has their own space and can also enjoy each other's company. The kitchen and dining area has bench seating which makes the area feel spacious and roomy. The kitchen island and walk-in pantry make mealtime a breeze. The backyard opens through the Pella sliding glass door and the abundance of shade from the trees provides year-round enjoyment. The home has an ideal location that provides easy access to NISD schools, restaurants, and entertainment. This would make a great home for everyone, whether for personal use or even as an income producing rental home!
